What is the name of the protein associated with PDB ID pdb:7A97, and in which species is its corresponding gene expressed?
sparql:
# Endpoint: https://rdfportal.org/sib/sparql
# Description: What is the name of the protein associated with PDB ID pdb:7A97, and in which species is its corresponding gene expressed?
# Parameter: uniprot_pdb: (example: pdb:7A97)

PREFIX genex: <http://purl.org/genex#>
PREFIX orth: <http://purl.org/net/orth#>
PREFIX lscr: <http://purl.org/lscr#>
PREFIX core: <http://purl.uniprot.org/core/>
PREFIX chembl: <http://rdf.ebi.ac.uk/terms/chembl#>
PREFIX obo: <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/>
PREFIX rdfspdb: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX pdb: <http://rdf.wwpdb.org/pdb/>

SELECT DISTINCT ?uniprot_recommended_name ?taxonomy_common_name 
WHERE {
    VALUES ?uniprot_pdb { pdb:7A97 }
    ?Gene a orth:Gene ;
        lscr:xrefUniprot / core:recommendedName / core:fullName ?uniprot_recommended_name ;
        orth:organism / obo:RO_0002162 / core:commonName ?taxonomy_common_name ;
        lscr:xrefUniprot / rdfspdb:seeAlso ?uniprot_pdb .
    ?uniprot_pdb a core:Structure_Resource .
}
LIMIT 100

user_question: At which developmental stages is the gene with the ORF name UNQ868/PRO1885 expressed?
sparql:
# Endpoint: https://rdfportal.org/sib/sparql
# Description: At which developmental stages is the gene with the ORF name UNQ868/PRO1885 expressed?
# Parameter: uniprot_orf_name: (example: UNQ868/PRO1885)

PREFIX genex: <http://purl.org/genex#>
PREFIX efo: <http://www.ebi.ac.uk/efo/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX orth: <http://purl.org/net/orth#>
PREFIX lscr: <http://purl.org/lscr#>
PREFIX core: <http://purl.uniprot.org/core/>
PREFIX chembl: <http://rdf.ebi.ac.uk/terms/chembl#>

SELECT DISTINCT ?expression_condition_developmental_stage 
WHERE {
    VALUES ?uniprot_orf_name { "UNQ868/PRO1885" }
    ?Expression a genex:Expression ;
        genex:hasExpressionCondition / genex:hasDevelopmentalStage / rdfs:label ?expression_condition_developmental_stage ;
        genex:hasSequenceUnit / lscr:xrefUniprot / core:encodedBy / core:orfName ?uniprot_orf_name .
}
LIMIT 100

# Endpoint: https://rdfportal.org/sib/sparql
# Description: What is the FDR p-value of the gene encoding the protein associated with PDB ID pdb:7A97?
# Parameter: uniprot_pdb: (example: pdb:7A97)

PREFIX genex: <http://purl.org/genex#>
PREFIX orth: <http://purl.org/net/orth#>
PREFIX lscr: <http://purl.org/lscr#>
PREFIX core: <http://purl.uniprot.org/core/>
PREFIX chembl: <http://rdf.ebi.ac.uk/terms/chembl#>
PREFIX rdfspdb: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX pdb: <http://rdf.wwpdb.org/pdb/>

SELECT DISTINCT ?expression_fdr_pvalue 
WHERE {
    VALUES ?uniprot_pdb { pdb:7A97 }
    ?Expression a genex:Expression ;
        genex:hasFDRpvalue ?expression_fdr_pvalue ;
        genex:hasSequenceUnit / lscr:xrefUniprot / rdfspdb:seeAlso ?uniprot_pdb .
    ?uniprot_pdb a core:Structure_Resource .
}
LIMIT 100
